items.title: Tiny Pacific nation to take up to 75 deportees as Trump administration accelerates mass removals
items.description: Palau, a small Pacific nation with 18,000 residents, agreed to accept U.S. deportees to address labor shortages. The deal includes millions in aid.

items.title: Kash Patel announces permanent closure of J. Edgar Hoover FBI Building for Reagan building move
